<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center lg:py-16 lg:px-12">
        <h2 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white">Where Ideas Find a Voice.</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg font-normal text-gray-500 lg:text-xl sm:px-16 xl:px-48 dark:text-gray-400">
          Welcome to IdeaSphere. Here at IdeaSphere, we believe every idea has the potential to spark change, inspire creativity, or simply bring a smile to someone’s day. Our platform is a melting pot of thoughts, stories, and knowledge, catering to a wide range of topics—from tech innovations to lifestyle hacks, travel tales to personal growth journeys. Whether you're seeking inspiration, looking to learn something new, or just here to enjoy a good read, we’re committed to delivering content that resonates with everyone. Join us as we explore the boundless world of ideas, one post at a time.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col mb-8 lg:mb-16 space-y-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
            <%= link_to posts_path do %>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                Go To Blogs
                <svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
              </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
